FT  04 AUG 93 / UK Company News: TR Pacific net assets rise
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
STRONG performances by south-east Asian stock markets, particularly Hong
Kong and Indonesia, contributed to a rise of 23.6 per cent in net asset
value at TR Pacific Investment Trust over the six months to June 30.
The figure of 141.7p compared with 114.63p in December and 95.3p a year
