Net revenue improved to Pounds 370,000 (Pounds 328,000) for earnings of
0.552p (0.49p) per share.
Plans to raise further equity finance have been under consideration since
the beginning of July, but directors said they were not proceeding
immediately.
The proposals will be kept under review.
The trust continues to be optimistic on the region's growth prospects. The
overheating economy in China may have a temporarily adverse effect on
sentiment, but directors see a good outlook for longer term investment.
