stocks Page 32
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>DEZ  Germany, EC.
    DKZ  Denmark, EC.
    BEZ  Belgium, EC.
    ESZ  Spain, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
